## Card schema registry (contract names)

These are **API/contract identifiers**. Field lists belong in **`agents/schemas/`** and TypeScript types — keep this table as the **index** only.

| Schema | Role |
|--------|------|
| `SHOPPING_CARD` | `recommendation`, `products[]` (name, price, rating, image URL, url, pros/cons, optional badge), `buyingGuide?` |
| `COMPARISON_CARD` | `options[]`, `criteria[]`, `winner`, `winnerReason`, scores per option |
| `PLACE_CARD` | `places[]` (address, rating, geo?, photo?, hours?, …), `mapCenter?` |
| `PERSON_CARD` | `name`, role, company, links, `bio?`, `photo?` only if confident |
| `MEETING_BRIEF` | `meetingWith`, company context, person background, `recentNews[]`, talking points, avoid list |
| `DRAFT_CARD` | `draftType`, `subject?`, `body`, `tone`, `assumptions?` |
| `DECISION_CARD` | `question`, `verdict`, `verdictReason`, `options[]`, `keyData[]`, `confidence` |
| `RESEARCH_CARD` | `topic`, executive `summary`, `keyFacts[]`, `sections?`, `sources[]` |
| `EXPLAIN_CARD` | `concept`, `tldr`, `explanation`, `steps?`, `analogy?`, `commonMistakes?` |
| `SUMMARY_CARD` | `tldr`, `keyPoints[]`, `pullQuote?`, `readingTime?`, source metadata |
| `IDEA_CARDS` | `context`, `ideas[]` (title, hook, angle, format?) |

Extend the registry in code when UX requires a new layout; update this table in the **same** change.

